data.description: Come see this large tri-level home in the highly sought after community of Pinehaven. This home has 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a bonus flex room currently used as a fourth bedroom. The garage has been converted into an entertainment space equipped with its own mini-split system. There is a large, covered,  screened-in back porch off the living room. The backyard is fully fenced with a gate entry door on either side of the house. The home does need some interior cosmetic updates and a new roof but the price offering reflects the material condition. So if you are searching for more house for your money in a great location with easy access to Charlotte then be sure not to miss out on this one. Make your appointment today to see the opportunity that awaits.
